========================================================================
EVIDENCE LAYOUT
========================================================================

/workspace/task/   SEED task directory (read-only). Unmodified editable file(s),
                   task_config.yaml, etc.
/workspace/run/    Executor's full workspace (read-only, adversarial). Treat
